Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了 對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.33,0:21:39.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.84,0:21:44.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.21,0:21:50.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.51,0:21:56.27,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.85,0:21:58.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hdc\3a&Hdc\4a&Hdc}Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.89,0:22:09.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.74,0:22:20.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.49,0:22:28.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.88,0:22:33.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.25,0:22:44.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是暗號的解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的提示卻暗藏巨大的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.40,0:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幫忙開發新玩具而獲得豐厚酬金的阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定帶著元太他們去玩尋寶遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是阿笠博士的叔父的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在叔父去世後的50年之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該不會有人進來的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻好像有人在這裡住過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還發現一些奇妙的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.84,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現花瓶或是盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有燭臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.43,0:02:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著星星、月亮跟太陽所組合而成的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而博士為了尋寶遊戲所藏的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部被某個人給弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得這個別墅好像隱藏著什麼巨大的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.26,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在別墅裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次找到7個畫有暗號的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法語字典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.21,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.47,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.16,0:02:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肖像畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿笠博士想起了從前阿姨給他看的那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有寄信人地址和名字的信件四周也有同樣的暗號圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.81,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些信還拿給推理小說家 也就是我的爸爸看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小說家發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些暗號全都是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.52,0:03:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來寫那些信和畫這裡的暗號應該是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.73,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人為什麼要寫那些暗號給我阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不想讓阿姨以外的人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如他正在被某人追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經你這麼一說 阿姨曾經說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個怪人經常偷她的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那傢伙就是弄壞玩具的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棟別墅果然不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太陽的秘密(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算知道這些暗號是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也還不知道是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不難 只要找出它的規律就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如黑色的太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的太陽 月亮 星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑色的月亮 星星裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有和它們相似的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有黑色太陽沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在平假名裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.91,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既無段也無行的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既無段也無行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ん」 是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色太陽原來就是代表ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要注意的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有暗號後面都有三個同樣的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這三個圖案和前面的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不同意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是在圖形旁的那些小黑點和小白點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右下角那個小黑點雖然還不知道是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過右上角的那些白點和黑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.83,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從位置上來看 很有可能是平假名的濁音和半濁音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是濁音和半濁音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前學校不是教過了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濁音就是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從が行 ざ行右上角的「"」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而半濁音就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぱぴぷぺぽ右上角的「。」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再配合暗號來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些往上翹的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黑點的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有白點的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有什麼都沒有的月亮 共三種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三種往上翹的月亮可能是は行裡的其中一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有濁音和半濁音的只有は行而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最容易讀的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫在這酒杯底的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掉前面三個 從第四個開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個黑色的太陽是ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個是ぱ行裡的其中一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.04,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個字而且其中有ん和ぱ行的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲 髮夾 鵜鶘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆麵包 香瓜麵包 咖哩麵包…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦 日本 電燈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是寫著「撲克牌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果是這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這燭臺上畫的暗號…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個字是ぷ 第四個字是ら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぷ… ら…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是螺旋槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果這個黑色的月亮是ろ的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暗號是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぷろぺら…ろ…ろ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.28,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みろ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看螺旋槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機的暗號就是畫在螺旋槳上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果右上方的黑點是「"」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個字是ぶ 第三個字是ら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぶら…をみろ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.25,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぶら…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油畫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看油畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指這幅肖像畫吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些暗號全是別墅裡的某一樣東西的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面加個「看」字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說跟著這個提示 就可以找到某樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是只能用暗號才能找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的某個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.97,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我們將所有的暗號解開 然後獲得寶藏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的藏有寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道是不是寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡一定隱藏著什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子上畫的暗號是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.75,0:07:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個字是ん 第二個字加有濁音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,か び ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字典上面的暗號是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ん…ろ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡娃娃上面的暗號是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わいんぐらす…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止知道的文字有17個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他空白部分用其他圖案來做推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在寫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是暗號的解讀表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看可以就發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽 月亮 星星分別代表「あいうえお」各段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.48,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後它們是根據同一規則橫向變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如太陽和星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們周圍尖尖的部分都是按順時針方向逐一減少一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而月亮也是按順時針方向缺角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於圖形右下角的黑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是圖形不夠用才加上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.68,0:09:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後利用這個解讀表把所有的暗號解讀出來 就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看燭臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看螺旋槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看油畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看法語詞典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說寶藏在暖爐裡面啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗號 刻在地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 把剛才的解讀表拿給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個暗號是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別賣關子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子… 是指最初的那個盤子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這樣不就又回到起點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被這些暗號給耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這討厭的惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇？ 怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人利用這種可能解不開的暗號惡作劇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果照著暗號來看就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個解讀表有什麼地方弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些暗號的順序之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼真正的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 在警方來這裡之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先把東西放回原來的位置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子是在碗櫃裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果把盤子 花瓶前面的那些字連起來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さがろぷあれにわとふだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是用羅馬拼音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燭臺是放在暖爐的上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架飛機是放在哪裡的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.92,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本來放在花瓶旁邊 是我拿到寢室裡面去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶的旁邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它想成英文呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 法語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是德文呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個想得明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要坐在房間中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得撲克牌好像也是在這房間裡面的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本放在時鐘的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿來用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫有暗號的東西全部都在這房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.27,0:12:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果將它們依照順序串聯起來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個是盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燭臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋槳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法語字典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線剛好集中在房間中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪步美一直在我旁邊走來走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了 房間中央就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一點可疑的地方也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在地板的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板的吊燈有條溝槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 快過來背我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.13,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓好像有什麼東西掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.06,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那間房間的正上方應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裡面竟然有樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個暗號是暗示天花板的吊燈有機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是指這個隱藏的樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說叔父喜歡玩這種機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然真的有這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道寶藏就在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面一定隱藏著什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把窗戶打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻中的一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是畫油畫的顏料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 桌子上好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 說清楚一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡住著一位手指靈活的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟畫暗號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是他這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他是被殺的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.38,0:16:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.12,0:16:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在寫信給你阿姨的時候去世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他的心臟好像不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他為什麼會在這個房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.95,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道這裡的應該只有住在這裡的叔父和阿姨才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有一個人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.70,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你叔父去世之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經在這裡出現過的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父去世之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暖爐旁邊的你阿姨和叔父的畫像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是畫那幅畫的畫家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他大概是在畫畫時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叔父提起過這個房間的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他為什麼要藏在這裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要用暗號信寄給阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想原因大概就是這個吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.02,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20元美鈔的範本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假鈔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.37,0:17:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是受人委託的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是後來他大概良心不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便和範本一起消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.04,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了躲那個人才偷偷住在這裡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信給你阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想感謝她讓他住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以用暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.63,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不想讓其他人知道他躲在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿姨說的那個偷信的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是製造假鈔的委託人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.47,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也是將博士藏起來的那些玩具給割壞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為可以找到那個範本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道裡面竟然是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我把它們給割爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說他和這裡的主人很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直懷疑他還躲在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還有這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們這些小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.93,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.36,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果打中範本的話 那就沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.40,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從老頭子手中拿範本過來給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.51,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我之後 叔叔會獎賞妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭…臭小子 存心找死嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急什麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.43,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西待會再給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧田倫明…先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體怎麼可能會說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.48,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔細聽的話就聽得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的亡靈一定還在這裡徘徊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭小子 挺大膽的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧田倫明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧田倫明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧田倫明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧田倫明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.29,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信守承諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把東西給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我們趁現在快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小心亡靈又跑回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個　這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人變聲器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我趁機錄下自己的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以慢速度重複播放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.35,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是怎麼知道他的名字的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桌上那封寫了一半的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的暗號寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.36,0:20:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不想把這件藝術品交給奧田倫明」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.91,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定想把這件藝術品交給阿姨保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.29,0:20:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才留下表明自己藏身在這別墅裡的暗號啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你阿姨現在人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年去世了 享年76歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還一直單身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.59,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是為了答謝她而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時後 警方趕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕了奧田倫明那個壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於可以回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.75,0:23:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸說的那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就像太陽一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.36,0:23:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後有一段時間 他都叫我太陽博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是指這件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.20,0:23:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是比喻而已啊 比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.09,0:23:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.47,0:23:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個解讀表解讀博士的名字看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.26,0:23:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.98,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是太陽博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.85,0:23:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…外面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我們兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連我們也騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.15,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.49,0:24:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.69,0:24:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團消失事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.85,0:24:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.02,0:24:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶的數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次偵探團大活躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是我
